p.e:
HI THERE, AND WELCOME TO WELCOME-TOWN!

THIS IS THE PLACE WHERE WE ALL CAN BUILD
TOGETHER - EVERYONE GETS EDIT RIGHTS HERE.
JUST ASK JOONGLE. IN THE FUTURE WE HOPE
THERE WILL BE AN OPEN AREA FUNCTION HERE
SO THAT NEW CITIZENS WILL BE ABLE TO EDIT
RIGHT AWAY.

THERE IS REALLY FEW RULES...JUST BE RESPECTFUL
OF OTHERS CREATIONS AND TRY NOT TO DESTROY
THE GROUND UNLESS YOU BUILD ANOTHER ONE.

BUILD WHEREVER YOU LIKE AND LETS MAKE THIS
PLACE HUGE AND COOL TOGETHER.
